function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	idActorClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(idActorNPC, true)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorClone) then
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idActorClone, idTaissaLookLoc, true)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(sConvTaissaChant, idSelf, idActorClone)
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idActorClone, "Taissa_Idle_Chant_Ritual_Strong_EyeLevel")
	end
	
	--Advance Quest
	Hydra.Wait(8)
	Hydra.EventSendToActor("TaissaRitualComplete", idSelf, idSelf)
end

followerTaissa = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Taissa_Witch_Follower")
if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerTaissa) then
	Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerTaissa)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerTaissa, false)
	Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(sConvGotItems, idSelf, followerTaissa)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(followerTaissa, sConvGotItems)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(followerTaissa, 0.5)
end
